Dataload, vocab builder are common files for without and with attention.

We have separate train.py,and model.py for attention and without attention. 
In case of attention, train.py has evaluate function included in it for testing purpose aswell. 


---(without attention)
Test.py gives bleu for the batch level 

Sample.py prints predicted caption and shows the input image. (only one sample image can be predicted in a run given the image id. ) 

------------


Dataset: https://drive.google.com/open?id=1bieOvBoDwcCyczVE57e9DL5_2e2nVUS2 
incase blackboard submission fails for data upload due to large size use this link to download the data. 